dct_description_sm: Compilation from mission flown in 1956. "Hundreds of Yatala and Adelaide." Relief shown by contour interval 25 feet. Datum Mean Sea Level Port Adealide. "Triangulation and traverse by S/A/Department of Lands, based on Sydney Observatory." "Photolitography by H. J. Wall, Government Photolithographer, Adelaide." Includes index to adjoining streets.
dct_creator_sm: South Australia. Office of the Surveyor General
